com.att.research.xacml.api.trace

Class TraceEngineFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.api.trace.TraceEngineFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoggingTraceEngineFactory, NullTraceEngineFactory

    public abstract class TraceEngineFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides methods for creating instances of the TraceEngine interface. This may be used by PDP, PEP, or PIP implementations to provide tracing facilities that are useful for validating that XACML Policies and PolicySets operate as expected.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Christopher A. Rath
